summary: Discover the ancient Ysgramor Tower if you are not afraid of heights and brave enough to jump from cliff to cliff at high altitude.
descriptionHtml:
Use your acrobatics skills to climb to the top and admire an astonishing view from the top. There you can find a chamber with food and bed to rest after a great effort.

In the chamber on the top there are barrels full of snacks that will get you ready for the next battle

Don\'t want go all the way down to reach the ground? No problem! Find a trapdoor in the chamber to get inside the tower and jump down to the water. But be careful! its an easy way to kill yourself ;)

Tower is located north-east from Falkret and can be seen from great distance

Have fun!
author: ireneuszpaszkiewicz
